data.description: Now is a fantastic time for your purchase into  one of the most desirable and popular Gulf Breeze communities.  Walk into this beautiful, almost new, craftsman style home and say WOW!  A rare find with 5 bedroom, 3 full baths, formal dining room and home office.  This spacious open floor plan offers a 9’ and 11’ ceilings, eye catching engineered vinyl flooring and upgraded carpet in the bedrooms.  The stunning kitchen is an entertainer’s delight and the heart of the home with a 9’ x 4’ kitchen island and seating to accommodate a crowd.  Covered front and back porches and large fenced backyard.   Built in 2022 this home still carries a transferable builder’s bond.  Located in one of the newest subdivision, that has underground utilities and a community pool. This is a gem you don’t want to miss out on.  Call your agent today.
